{"tid":649361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩同班朋友食面，女朋友竟然叫豬雜面食","createTime":"2018-05-01T13:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T13:39:52.000Z","uid":82845,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0d954431b831f345f66a8f6a1e7c1d12643d9c","tid":649361,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"我頭先帶埋女朋友同班朋友打羽毛球，打完一齊去諗住食碗麵，食完返屋企沖個涼放低啲野再同佢地去睇戲。<br />\n<br />\n點知佢好地地走去叫左碗豬雜麵食，平時最多都係食牛腩麵，真係好鬼失禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個friend條女人地都係叫雲吞麵。私底下同佢食都無所謂呀，而家係我啲朋友面前叫豬雜麵真係好肉酸，仲要成碗食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ecccd9ae11db37768acdaf5025f52d8b230b9e","tid":649361,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6eade11fc30073d32a799dfa7a34fef994a19b8","tid":649361,"uid":8175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"係我就打鳩佢啦"},{"pid":"de558830eb3e6ae608301455d072891d2596228f","tid":649361,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"我咪同左你講我食緊麵嗰陣你唔好嗌我個名，分手啦。"},{"pid":"7d113da0ce0dbec30ae4a352406befaf5659fef6","tid":649361,"uid":113467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"你條女俾你溝到仲失禮啦"},{"pid":"0ae967d5afec3ef2e033d5daf08afb9f8ea438e3","tid":649361,"uid":168280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6784d1a92de05901a4509558fc141b345c27d0","tid":649361,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:37:36.000Z","msg":"我ex同啲fd食牛撚牛波子添<br />\n仲要成班笑9我唔敢食<br />\n<br />\n利：比佢飛9左"},{"pid":"e76e5909ff14a9cfc319cf90e2c6f4481cf24201","tid":649361,"uid":180035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB